    <p>This is a 30-minute video shared by Ray Dalio on YouTube after the 2008 US financial crisis, 'How The Economic Machine Works', which has been viewed over 5 million times.</p>
    
    <p>Bill Gates' recommendation for this video:</p>
    
    <blockquote>
        "This knowledge would help everyone as investors and citizens. Watching it for 30 minutes is a worthwhile investment."
    </blockquote>
    
